snippet.title: FNaF SB: Blast to the Past! | Get Out! Chase
snippet.description:
Run Run Run! Happy Holidays, and a late 3 years to Security Breach.

What's old is new again.

Blast to the Past! is a mod that restores all cut content back to Security Breach and takes a step further by adding new content and new gameplay features and bits of story to help rekindle the spark that is Security Breach! 

This teaser is one of our favorites, jump, duck, and trip as you race to Get Out! Featuring Montgomery Gator’s Death taunt on the Game Over screen, rendered in real time!

A lot of it has been sitting on the back burner for a while now and we wanted to show something off. Despite jobs, school, and personal commitments, the mod continues to grow.

It may be a slow cook, but the meal is always delicious. Stay tuned in 2025 for some big announcements! We have been dying to announce plans and you don't want to miss out!

Have a Faz-errific day and keep a look out for teasers and the future release!
